@startuml
title Modern Data Architecture - Deployment Sequence

actor "DevOps Engineer" as DevOps
participant "Docker Compose" as DC
participant "PostgreSQL\nContainer" as PG
participant "pgAdmin\nContainer" as PGADMIN
participant "Nginx\nContainer" as NGINX
participant "Airbyte\nContainer" as AIRBYTE
participant "DBT\nContainer" as DBT
participant "Superset\nContainer" as SUPERSET
database "PostgreSQL\nData Volume" as PGVOL
database "pgAdmin\nData Volume" as ADMINVOL

DevOps -> DC: docker-compose up -f Postgres-DWH/docker-compose.yml
activate DC

DC -> PGVOL: Create/Mount Volume
activate PGVOL
PGVOL --> DC: Volume Ready
deactivate PGVOL

DC -> PG: Deploy PostgreSQL Container
activate PG
PG -> PGVOL: Mount Data Volume
PG -> PG: Initialize Database
PG --> DC: PostgreSQL Running
deactivate PG

DC -> ADMINVOL: Create/Mount Volume
activate ADMINVOL
ADMINVOL --> DC: Volume Ready
deactivate ADMINVOL

DC -> PGADMIN: Deploy pgAdmin Container
activate PGADMIN
PGADMIN -> ADMINVOL: Mount Data Volume
PGADMIN -> PGADMIN: Initialize pgAdmin
PGADMIN --> DC: pgAdmin Running
deactivate PGADMIN

DC --> DevOps: PostgreSQL & pgAdmin Deployed
deactivate DC

DevOps -> DC: docker-compose up -f Postgres-DWH/docker-compose-nginx.yml
activate DC

DC -> NGINX: Build & Deploy Nginx Container
activate NGINX
NGINX -> NGINX: Load nginx.conf
NGINX -> PGADMIN: Configure Reverse Proxy
NGINX --> DC: Nginx Running
deactivate NGINX

DC --> DevOps: Nginx Proxy Deployed
deactivate DC

DevOps -> DC: Deploy Airbyte (via submodule)
activate DC
DC -> AIRBYTE: Deploy Airbyte Container
activate AIRBYTE
AIRBYTE -> AIRBYTE: Initialize Airbyte Services
AIRBYTE -> PG: Configure Connection
AIRBYTE --> DC: Airbyte Running
deactivate AIRBYTE
DC --> DevOps: Airbyte Deployed
deactivate DC

DevOps -> DC: Deploy DBT (via submodule)
activate DC
DC -> DBT: Deploy DBT Container
activate DBT
DBT -> DBT: Load DBT Project Configuration
DBT -> PG: Configure Target Connection
DBT --> DC: DBT Running
deactivate DBT
DC --> DevOps: DBT Deployed
deactivate DC

DevOps -> DC: Deploy Superset (via submodule)
activate DC
DC -> SUPERSET: Deploy Superset Container
activate SUPERSET
SUPERSET -> SUPERSET: Initialize Superset Services
SUPERSET -> PG: Configure Database Connection
SUPERSET --> DC: Superset Running
deactivate SUPERSET
DC --> DevOps: Superset Deployed
deactivate DC

DevOps -> DevOps: Verify All Services Running

note right of DevOps
  Alternative deployment option:
  Python script (Source/script.py)
  can be used for direct CSV loading
  into PostgreSQL using .env configuration
end note

@enduml
